'''Dave Thomas''' is a computer programmer and author/editor.  He has written about [[Ruby programming language|Ruby]].

Dave and partner [[Andy Hunt (author)|Andy Hunt]] wrote [[The Pragmatic Programmer]] and run [[Pragmatic Bookshelf|The Pragmatic Bookshelf]] publishing company.

Dave Thomas lives in [[Flower Mound, Texas]]. He moved to the United States from England in 1994.

Dave has also coined the phrase '[[Code Kata]]'.

He studied [[computer science]] at [[Imperial College London]].<ref>{{cite web
